file.name: schema-without-properties.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Schema with no properties
servers:
  - url: http://localhost
paths:
  /no-props:
    get:
      operationId: noProps
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Response object with no properties
          content:
            'application/json':
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  example:
                    type: string
                  no_properties:
                    type: object
